channel.title: Hellz Scape V1 [Delta] [Customs] [First Release] [1092+ Downloads!]
channel.description:
I. Introduction
Hello, This is my first release Hellz Scape V1. Here is the download link to my twin pack (Client, and source.) Download Link: http://www.mediafire.com/?sharekey=216e96a8bad1c74e312dbd5f2bdc5062e04e75f6e8ebb871 Please comment. My goal was to have V2 out when I got to around 500 downloads. The count is at about 490, more when I check tomorrow, and V2 will not be ready for a while. I just want to thank the 490+ people who downloaded the server, I hope you all enjoy it.
Note -- I give no permission for anyone to copy and paste this on any other forum. If you see Hellz Scape posted on any forums please report it to me.
Note -- Thank you everyone who has downloaded Hellz Scape V1. Hellz Scape V2 is very different, at this rate I doubt I will have V2 ready at 1,000 downloads. Also once the download count reaches 1,000 I will quickly finish V2, though only if I am not finished, if I already finished V2 I might do something else.
II. Glossary:
I - Introduction II - Glossary III - Description of server IV - Pictures V. Custom Items List VI - Credits
III. Description of the server.
The server is based off XScape, which is based off Delta. It has semi-working pest control, which I hope to take further in V2. It has a decent Barbarian Assault, which will change in V2. It has about 20 custom items, which will grow in V2. It is based in Edgeville, which has the possibility of changing in V2. Godwars will become harder in V2. The server is a base server for my source to start growing. If you host, please give me some credit. In V2 I hope that it will not be recognizable as a Delta server. New training, new barrows, and much more in V2!
IV. Pictures. http://img18.imageshack.us/gal.php?g=newbitmapimagecopy.png [img]http://img15.imageshack.us/img15/7972/newbitmapimagecopy.png[/img] [img]http://img16.imageshack.us/img16/7421/newbitmapimagecopy2.png[/img] [img]http://img22.imageshack.us/img22/994/newbitmapimagecopy3.png[/img] [img]http://img7.imageshack.us/img7/6470/newbitmapimagecopy4.png[/img] [img]http://img7.imageshack.us/img7/2238/newbitmapimagecopy5.png[/img] [img]http://img13.imageshack.us/img13/569/newbitmapimagenewbitmap.png[/img] [img]http://img19.imageshack.us/img19/569/newbitmapimagenewbitmap.png[/img] [img]http://img21.imageshack.us/img21/569/newbitmapimagenewbitmap.png[/img] [img]http://img27.imageshack.us/img27/569/newbitmapimagenewbitmap.png[/img] [IMG]http://img26.imageshack.us/img26/569/newbitmapimagenewbitmap.png[/img] [IMG]http://i39.tinypic.com/w9tw9e.jpg[/img]
V. Custom Item List [code]15507 - Dragon Whip 15510 - Sacred Whip 15509 - Devil's Whip 15600 - Gold partyhat 15601 - Devil's partyhat 15602 - Dragon Cape - Not in pictures 15603 - Beautiful Cape - Not in pictures 15604 - Danger Cape- Not in pictures 15605 - Bronze Whip 15606 - Iron Whip 15607 - Steel Whip 15608 - Black whip 15609 - Mithril Whip 15610 - Adamant Whip 15611 - Rune Whip 15700 - Devil's Platelegs 15701 - Devil's Platebody 15702 - Devil's Kiteshield 15703 - Devil's Cape 15704 - Devil's Gloves 15705 - Devil's Boots 8002 - Dragon Claws -- Spec I do not think works[/code]
VI. Credits
25% -- Delta 10% -- XScape source creator 30% -- Mopar Server Help Forum 35% -- Me
Note -- Please private message me all the glitches, bugs, and errors you find in the server. Thank you. Note -- Customs were not released into the game VIA monsters, only VIA spawning. This is up to you.
What to expect in V2 -- More realistic bonuses. More customs Different training areas Better mini games More in general!
Have any questions on my server, or in general feel free to send me an offline IM at HellzScape@Live.Com
Currently on V1.1 or V2: Color Key: Red -- Did not start, or very little. Orange -- Started, but not a lot. Yellow -- About half way completed. Limegreen -- Almost done. Green -- Finished.
Slayer -- 0% Moving things around -- 100% Adding customs into the server -- 12.5% Adding customs into drops-- 75%% Running into some errors, not sure what... Postponed. [Color=green]New never before seen Mining area -- 100%[/color] [Color=green]Fixing up shops -- 100%[/color] [Color=green]Fishing Guild, With 63 fishing required. Accessible by portal from home. -- 100%[/color] [Color=green]A new, never before seen, mining area. -- 100%[/color] [Color=Green]Fixing Dragonbolts (e) to hit 60s -- 100%[/color] -- I don't know the max hit, but so far it's a 38.
